description: Request verification to get more features for your server. *(Server owner only)*
large_description:
Verification will allow your server to get access to more commands and features.

To get verification, you need to follow the following requirements:
- Have 200+ Members.
- Actively use the bot.
- Not a 'Shitposting' or bot server.

Spamming this command in order to verified quicker will lower your chances.
